OL,5,Chatred
OL,7,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,8,Fsaid it has authorised South Wales
OL,9,FPolice to charge two men over Facebook
OL,10,Fposts which allegedly intended to stir
OL,11,Fup racial or religious hatred.
OL,13,FGeraint Boyce, 43, and Jamie Michael,
OL,14,F45, are accused of publishing
OL,15,Fthreatening material on a Facebook
OL,16,Faccount, contrary to Section 29C(1) of
OL,17,Fthe Public Order Act 1986.
